summary: I have always been interested in art since I was a child. Especially painting has always been an important part of my life. Even when I was a little girl, I knew that I would do my education in this subject. I am also interested in other aspects of art. I have a movie collection and I like to take analog photos. Anything related to art and design interests me. For the rest, I am an animal rights advocate. You can take a look at the information of the animal rights association, of which I am the Co-Founder, in the my experiences section. I don't know what else to say about myself. This much from me. I hope you are having a nice day, take care. :)
